<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{{title}}</title>
  <meta name="description" content="{{description}}">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon.png?v=20260331c">
  <link href="/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="/css/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="/css/templatemo-first-portfolio-style.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --app-ink: #17212b;
      --app-muted: #607080;
      --app-primary: #535da1;
      --app-primary-dark: #3e4781;
      --app-green: #14b789;
      --app-line: rgba(23, 33, 43, 0.12);
      --app-soft: #f5f8fc;
      --app-shadow: 0 18px 46px rgba(23, 33, 43, 0.10);
    }

    body { background: #f6f8fb; color: var(--app-ink); }
    .app-page { padding-top: 112px; overflow: hidden; }
    .app-band { padding: 74px 24px; }
    .app-inner { width: min(1140px, 100%); margin: 0 auto; }
    .app-hero {
      min-height: calc(100vh - 112px);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      background:
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(246, 248, 251, 0.98), rgba(246, 248, 251, 0.88) 56%, rgba(246, 248, 251, 0.70)),
        url("/images/generated/screencam-hero-bg.png") center / cover no-repeat;
    }
    .app-hero-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) 370px; gap: 56px; align-items: center; }
    .app-kicker { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 9px; min-height: 32px; padding: 5px 12px; border: 1px solid rgba(83,93,161,.18); border-radius: 8px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.75); color: var(--app-primary-dark); font-size: .78rem; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: .06em; text-transform: uppercase; }
    .app-hero h1 { margin: 22px 0 18px; font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 5rem); line-height: 1; letter-spacing: 0; }
    .app-hero p { max-width: 680px; color: #344353; font-size: 1.08rem; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0 0 28px; }
    .app-actions { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
    .app-btn { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 9px; min-height: 48px; padding: 11px 20px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 900; text-decoration: none; border: 1px solid transparent; }
    .app-btn.primary { background: var(--app-primary); color: #fff; box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(83,93,161,.23); }
    .app-btn.primary:hover { background: var(--app-primary-dark); color: #fff; }
    .app-btn.secondary { background: rgba(255,255,255,.78); border-color: rgba(83,93,161,.28); color: var(--app-primary-dark); }
    .app-btn.secondary:hover { background: #fff; color: var(--app-primary-dark); }
    .app-device { border: 1px solid var(--app-line); border-radius: 8px; background: #fff; box-shadow: var(--app-shadow); overflow: hidden; }
    .app-device-bar { height: 46px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 0 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--app-line); }
    .app-device-title { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; font-weight: 900; font-size: .9rem; }
    .app-device-title i { color: var(--app-primary); }
    .app-dots { display: flex; gap: 6px; }
    .app-dots span { width: 9px; height: 9px; border-radius: 50%; background: #d8dde6; }
    .app-device-screen { padding: 24px; min-height: 310px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(83,93,161,.92), rgba(24,116,196,.82)); color: #fff; display: grid; align-content: end; }
    .app-device-screen h2 { margin: 0 0 10px; color: #fff; font-size: 2rem; }
    .app-device-screen p { margin: 0; color: rgba(255,255,255,.84); line-height: 1.6; }
    .app-proof { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px; margin-top: 24px; }
    .app-proof-pill { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; min-height: 34px; padding: 6px 11px; border-radius: 8px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.78); border: 1px solid rgba(23,33,43,.10); color: #344353; font-size: .82rem; font-weight: 900; }
    .app-proof-pill.downloads { color: #0e8a63; border-color: rgba(20,183,137,.35); background: rgba(20,183,137,.11); }
    .app-section-heading { max-width: 760px; margin-bottom: 34px; }
    .app-section-heading .app-kicker { margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .app-section-heading h2 { margin: 0; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.8vw, 3rem); line-height: 1.12; }
    .app-section-heading p { margin: 14px 0 0; color: var(--app-muted); line-height: 1.75; }
    .app-white { background: #fff; }
    .app-soft { background: var(--app-soft); }
    .app-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: 18px; }
    .app-card, .app-price-card, .app-contact-card { border: 1px solid var(--app-line); border-radius: 8px; background: #fff; box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(23,33,43,.06); }
    .app-card { padding: 22px; min-height: 190px; }
    .app-card i { display: inline-grid; place-items: center; width: 42px; height: 42px; margin-bottom: 18px; border-radius: 8px; background: rgba(83,93,161,.10); color: var(--app-primary); font-size: 1.2rem; }
    .app-card h3 { margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 1.02rem; }
    .app-card p { margin: 0; color: var(--app-muted); font-size: .9rem; line-height: 1.65; }
    .app-price-layout, .app-contact-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) 390px; gap: 34px; align-items: start; }
    .app-included { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: 12px; padding: 0; margin: 0; list-style: none; }
    .app-included li { display: flex; gap: 9px; color: #344353; line-height: 1.55; }
    .app-included i { color: var(--app-green); margin-top: 2px; }
    .app-price-card { padding: 28px; border-color: rgba(83,93,161,.35); box-shadow: var(--app-shadow); }
    .app-price { display: flex; align-items: baseline; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 7px 12px; margin: 16px 0 10px; }
    .app-price strong { color: var(--app-ink); font-size: 3.1rem; line-height: 1; }
    .app-price span { color: var(--app-muted); font-weight: 900; }
    .app-old-price { color: var(--app-muted); font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 900; text-decoration: line-through; text-decoration-thickness: 2px; }
    .app-note { margin: 0 0 20px; color: var(--app-muted); line-height: 1.65; }
    .app-contact-card { padding: 24px; }
    .app-contact-list { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: 14px; }
    .app-contact-link { min-height: 118px; padding: 18px; border: 1px solid var(--app-line); border-radius: 8px; color: var(--app-ink); text-decoration: none; }
    .app-contact-link:hover { color: var(--app-ink); border-color: rgba(83,93,161,.38); box-shadow: 0 14px 28px rgba(23,33,43,.08); }
    .app-contact-link i { display: inline-grid; place-items: center; width: 38px; height: 38px; margin-bottom: 12px; border-radius: 8px; background: rgba(83,93,161,.10); color: var(--app-primary); }
    .app-contact-link strong, .app-contact-link span { display: block; }
    .app-contact-link span { color: var(--app-muted); font-size: .86rem; margin-top: 6px; line-height: 1.5; }
    @media (max-width: 991px) {
      .app-page { padding-top: 190px; }
      .app-hero { min-height: auto; }
      .app-hero-grid, .app-price-layout, .app-contact-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .app-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
    }
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .app-band { padding: 48px 18px; }
      .app-actions .app-btn { width: 100%; }
      .app-grid, .app-included, .app-contact-list { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <section class="preloader"><div class="spinner"><span class="spinner-rotate"></span></div></section>
  <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-split">
    <div class="container">
      <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#appNav"><span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span></button>
      <a class="navbar-brand mx-auto mx-lg-0" href="/">JustAidyn</a>
      <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="appNav">
        <div class="navbar-split-layout w-100">
          <div class="navbar-top-contact d-none d-lg-flex">
            <div class="navbar-top-contact-left"></div>
            <div class="navbar-top-tools">
              <div class="language-selector navbar-top-lang language-flags" role="group" aria-label="Language selector">
                <button type="button" class="lang-flag-btn" data-lang-option="kk" onclick="changeLanguage('kk')" aria-label="Kazakh" title="Kazakh">KK</button>
                <button type="button" class="lang-flag-btn" data-lang-option="en" onclick="changeLanguage('en')" aria-label="English" title="English">EN</button>
                <button type="button" class="lang-flag-btn" data-lang-option="ru" onclick="changeLanguage('ru')" aria-label="Russian" title="Russian">RU</button>
              </div>
              <div class="navbar-top-auth-links"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ul class="navbar-nav ms-lg-0 nav-row-primary">
            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/apps">Apps</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link active" href="#top">{{heroTitle}}</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#features">Features</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#pricing">Pricing</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="app-page" id="top">
    <section class="app-band app-hero">
      <div class="app-inner app-hero-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="app-kicker"><i class="bi bi-grid-3x3-gap"></i> JustAidyn Apps</div>
          <h1>{{heroTitle}}</h1>
          <p>{{heroText}}</p>
          <div class="app-actions">
            <a class="app-btn primary" href="{{primaryAction.url}}"><i class="bi bi-download"></i> {{primaryAction.label}}</a>
            <a class="app-btn secondary" href="#pricing"><i class="bi bi-credit-card"></i> See pricing</a>
            <a class="app-btn secondary" href="#contact"><i class="bi bi-envelope"></i> Contact</a>
          </div>
          <div class="app-proof">
            <span class="app-proof-pill downloads"><i class="bi bi-download"></i> {{downloadCount}} downloads</span>
            <span class="app-proof-pill"><i class="bi bi-tag"></i> Version {{releaseVersion}}</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <aside class="app-device" aria-label="{{heroTitle}} product preview">
          <div class="app-device-bar">
            <div class="app-device-title"><i class="bi bi-app-indicator"></i> {{heroTitle}}</div>
            <div class="app-dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="app-device-screen">
            <h2>Version {{releaseVersion}}</h2>
            <p>{{releaseNotes}}</p>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="app-band app-white" id="features">
      <div class="app-inner">
        <div class="app-section-heading">
          <div class="app-kicker"><i class="bi bi-stars"></i> Features</div>
          <h2>Product page structure for every JustAidyn program.</h2>
          <p>{{description}}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="app-grid">
          {{#each features}}
          <article class="app-card">
            <i class="bi {{this.icon}}"></i>
            <h3>{{this.title}}</h3>
            <p>{{this.text}}</p>
          </article>
          {{/each}}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="app-band app-soft" id="pricing">
      <div class="app-inner app-price-layout">
        <div>
          <div class="app-section-heading">
            <div class="app-kicker"><i class="bi bi-credit-card"></i> Pricing</div>
            <h2>{{pricingTitle}}</h2>
            <p>{{pricingText}}</p>
          </div>
          <ul class="app-included">
            {{#each included}}
            <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i><span>{{this}}</span></li>
            {{/each}}
          </ul>
        </div>
        <aside class="app-price-card">
          <div class="app-kicker"><i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i> {{planName}}</div>
          <div class="app-price"><strong>{{price}}</strong><span>{{pricePeriod}}</span>{{#if oldPrice}}<span class="app-old-price">{{oldPrice}}</span>{{/if}}</div>
          <p class="app-note">{{pricingNote}}</p>
          <div class="app-actions">
            <a class="app-btn primary" href="{{primaryAction.url}}"><i class="bi bi-download"></i> {{primaryAction.label}}</a>
            <a class="app-btn secondary" href="/subscription-terms"><i class="bi bi-file-text"></i> Terms</a>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="app-band app-white" id="contact">
      <div class="app-inner app-contact-layout">
        <div>
          <div class="app-section-heading">
            <div class="app-kicker"><i class="bi bi-life-preserver"></i> Contact</div>
            <h2>Support for setup, billing, and product questions.</h2>
            <p>Contact JustAidyn through the channel that fits the request. For account issues, include the email used for Google sign-in.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="app-contact-card">
            <div class="app-contact-list">
              <a class="app-contact-link" href="mailto:aidyn.daulet@gmail.com"><i class="bi bi-envelope"></i><strong>Email</strong><span>Detailed support and billing questions.</span></a>
              <a class="app-contact-link" href="https://wa.me/77769889889" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i class="bi bi-whatsapp"></i><strong>WhatsApp</strong><span>Quick product and setup questions.</span></a>
              <a class="app-contact-link" href="https://t.me/justaidyn" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i class="bi bi-telegram"></i><strong>Telegram</strong><span>Short questions and release updates.</span></a>
              <a class="app-contact-link" href="/refunds"><i class="bi bi-receipt"></i><strong>Refund policy</strong><span>Subscription and cancellation terms.</span></a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <aside class="app-price-card">
          <div class="app-kicker"><i class="bi bi-download"></i> Latest release</div>
          <div class="app-price"><strong>{{releaseVersion}}</strong><span>current version</span></div>
          <p class="app-note"><strong>{{downloadCount}}</strong> tracked downloads for this program.</p>
          <p class="app-note">Old installers are replaced when a new version is published. The download button always points to the latest available release.</p>
          <a class="app-btn primary" href="{{primaryAction.url}}"><i class="bi bi-download"></i> Download latest</a>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  {{> footer}}
  <script src="/js/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/jquery.sticky.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/custom.js?v=20260428-profile-i18n"></script>
</body>
</html>
